text: The 2013 AFC U-19 Women's Championship took place in 11–20 October 2013. ==Australia== Coach: Spencer Prior The final squad was named on 27 September 2013. ==China== Coach: Wang Jun ==Myanmar== Coach: Radov Minkovski ==North Korea== Coach: Hwang Yong-bong ==Japan== Coach: Hiroshi Yoshida The final squad was named on 26 September 2013. ==South Korea== Coach: Jong Song-chon The final squad was named on 1 October 2013. ==References== Category:2013 AFC U-19 Women's Championship Category:2013 in youth sport
title: 2013 AFC U-19 Women's Championship squads
